<br>
You have made open raids truly become the Open Raid Community.<br>
<br>
It has dawned on me over the last week that I for one have abused the system by signing up when I felt like raiding, whereas you deserve more commitment from those of us that have benefitted from your hard work.  Consequently I will now always strive to be available to Sunday Open Raid Community activities, whatever the objective, and I will accept that you wont always have space for me.<br>
<br>
Joining one of your raids is not a right, its a privilege. <p>Lord Regent <b>Gray Hateborn</b><br>
